The paper discusses the use of Grid infrastructures for collaborative clinical analysis of medical images, which involves the provision of a clinician-facing front-end workstation and the ability to service real-world clinician queries across a distributed and federated database. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Databases (cs.DB), Cybersecurity and Privacy (cs.CYBER), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), and Graphics (cs.GR).
